Package org.neo4j.internal.schema

Class NoSchemaDescriptor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.neo4j.internal.schema.NoSchemaDescriptor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SchemaDescriptor, SchemaDescriptorSupplier
    class NoSchemaDescriptor
extends Object
implements SchemaDescriptor
    A schema descriptor sentinel used for signalling the absence of a real schema descriptor.

    The instance is acquired via the SchemaDescriptor.noSchema() method.
